---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---

<LegalLayout
  title="About Us - Lingo7 Realty"
  description="Lingo7 Realty helps non-native English speakers pass the Florida real estate licensing exam - with parallel translation, audio, and spaced repetition built right into the material. Our mission: never let language stand between you and your license."
  canonicalUrl="https://lingo7realty.com/about/"
>
  <section class="about-hero">
    <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="" class="about-hero__icon" />
    <h1 class="about-hero__title">Our <span>mission</span></h1>
    <p class="about-hero__subtitle">To make sure language never stands between you and your real estate license.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="story">

    <div class="story__block">
      <span class="story__label">Where we came from</span>
      <h2>We grew out of <span>language learning</span></h2>
      <p>Lingo7 is an app for learning foreign languages. We turn hard text into text you understand. The translation is always one tap away. Every word is read aloud in a real human voice. And what you learn comes back to you just before you would forget it.</p>
      <p>For years we have helped people learn a new language. So we know how language gets in the way of smart, motivated people.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="story__block" style="margin-top: 56px;">
      <span class="story__label">The problem</span>
      <h2>Language shouldn't cost you a <span>career</span></h2>
      <p>On professional exams, and in real estate most of all, people do not fail because of the subject. They fail because of the English. The book, the questions, the answers are all in a second language. You spend your energy on the words, not on the material.</p>
      <p>We saw this happen again and again. And we knew our work in language learning could fix it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="story__highlight">
      <p>So we moved into exam prep. We took everything we know about language and <span>built it right into the exam material</span>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="story__block">
      <span class="story__label">The solution</span>
      <h2>Exam prep with <span>no language barrier</span></h2>
      <p>Lingo7 Realty is made so that anyone whose first language is not English can study well and with confidence. Every part of the material comes with a translation and audio in your own language. Term cards and questions stay in your memory through spaced repetition. And the tests take you to a passing score the fastest way.</p>
      <p>The subject comes first. Language stops standing between you and your license.</p>
    </div>

  </section>
</LegalLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .about-hero {
    padding: 160px 40px 80px;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #fff 100%);
  }
  .about-hero__icon {
    width: 72px; height: 72px;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
  }
  .about-hero__title {
    font-size: 52px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .about-hero__title span { color: #34D399; }
  .about-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: 21px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Story */
  .story {
    padding: 80px 40px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .story__block {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }
  .story__block:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .story__label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #34D399;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .story__block h2 {
    font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .story__block h2 span { color: #34D399; }
  .story__block p {
    font-size: 18px; color: #444; line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .story__block p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* Highlight quote */
  .story__highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #ecfdf5 100%);
    border-left: 4px solid #34D399;
    border-radius: 0 16px 16px 0;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    margin: 40px 0;
  }
  .story__highlight p {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .story__highlight span { color: #34D399; }

  /* Divider */
  .divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 3px;
    background: #34D399;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero { padding: 110px 16px 60px; }
    .about-hero__icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .about-hero__title { font-size: 34px; }
    .about-hero__subtitle { font-size: 17px; }
    .story { padding: 48px 16px; }
    .story__block h2 { font-size: 26px; }
    .story__block p { font-size: 16px; }
    .story__highlight { padding: 20px 20px; }
    .story__highlight p { font-size: 17px; }
  }
</style>
